eitc_phase_in.final_code:
variable eitc_phase_in_credit:
  entity: TaxUnit
  period: Year
  dtype: Money
  label: "EITC phase-in credit"
  citation: "26 USC § 32(a)(1)"

  references:
    earned_income: us/irs/income/earned_income
    n_qualifying_children: us/irs/eitc/n_qualifying_children
    phase_in_rate: param.irs.eitc.phase_in_rate
    earned_income_amount: param.irs.eitc.earned_income_amount

  formula:
    min(earned_income, earned_income_amount[n_qualifying_children]) * phase_in_rate[n_qualifying_children]

standard_deduction.final_code:
variable standard_deduction:
  entity: TaxUnit
  period: Year
  dtype: Money
  label: "Standard deduction"
  citation: "26 USC § 63(c)"

  references:
    is_joint: us/irs/filing_status/is_joint
    is_separate: us/irs/filing_status/is_separate  
    is_head_of_household: us/irs/filing_status/is_head_of_household
    is_single: us/irs/filing_status/is_single

  formula:
    is_joint * 29200 + is_head_of_household * 21900 + (1 - is_joint - is_head_of_household) * 14600

ctc_base.final_code:
variable child_tax_credit:
  entity: TaxUnit
  period: Year
  dtype: Money
  label: "Child Tax Credit under 26 USC § 24(a)"
  citation: "26 USC § 24(a)"

  references:
    n_qualifying_children: us/irs/ctc/n_qualifying_children

  formula:
    n_qualifying_children * 2000

salt_cap.final_code:
variable salt_deduction_limitation:
  entity: TaxUnit
  period: Year
  dtype: Money
  label: "SALT deduction limitation for taxable years 2018-2025"
  citation: "26 USC § 164(b)(6)"

  formula:
    10000

savers_credit.final_code:
variable eitc:
  entity: TaxUnit
  period: Year
  dtype: Money
  label: "Earned Income Tax Credit"
  citation: "26 USC § 32"

  references:
    earned_income: us/irs/income/earned_income
    n_qualifying_children: us/irs/eitc/n_qualifying_children
    phase_in_rate: param.irs.eitc.phase_in_rate
    max_credit: param.irs.eitc.max_credit

  formula:
    earned_income * phase_in_rate[n_qualifying_children]
